snippet.title: Bahamut and the Waqwaq Tree Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover a once-thriving ocean, now tainted by enigmatic dark entities. Decipher the mystery and rekindle the ocean's radiant light in Bahamut and the Waqwaq Tree, an underwater adventure game inspired by Arabian and Middle Eastern mythology!

🐤TWITTER: @StarvaniaStudio
🔗WEBSITE: Bahamutgame.com
